==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Tartareous
<hw>Tar*ta"re*ous</hw>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[Cf. 1st
<er>Tartarous</er>.]</ety> <sn>1.</sn> <def>Consisting of tartar; of the
nature of tartar.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <fld>(Bot.)</fld> <def>Having the surface rough and
crumbling; <as>as, many lichens are <ex>tartareous</ex></as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

